---
title: Quick Indian Mango Chicken & Rapid Rice with Garlicky Veggies & Yoghurt
description: Bold and mild North Indian spices coats diced chicken in this quick and easy Indian-inspired dish! With a bit of help from the
yoghurt and apricot sauce toppings, the aromas will make you want to dig in before this hits the table.
